ata transfer</li><li>KVM/SolusVM</li></ul><p>Jonathan has also prepared some special Xen HVM plans that can be customised, and promo code <b>XEN50OFF</b> that get you <b>50% off</b> recurring discount \u2014 including configuration options! So I am able to get the following system up for <b>\u00a34.08/month</b> (~USD$6.70).</p><ul><li>512MB memory (from configuration options)</li><li>16GB storage</li><li>160GB/month data transfer</li><li>Xen HVM/SolusVM</li></ul><p><a href=\"https://secure.thehosthouse.co.uk/cart.php?gid=15\">Here is the link</a> where all the offers are. Jonathan has even included the actual coupon codes on the page to make sure you don\u2019t pay full price! :) Servers in UK. Do check <a href=\"/blog/thehosthouse-2-97-256mb-kvm-vps-in-uk/\">previous post</a> where you\u2019ll find discussions and benchmarks. They have also done quite a bit of work on offering FreeBSD to their customers. FreeBSD 8.2 is now available, and their own local FreeBSD repository. Jonathan has been in business since 2003 (at Sipero.com).</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fthehosthouse-4-06-512mb-xen-hvm-vps-in-uk%2F&amp;t=TheHostHouse%20-%20%C2%A34.06%20512MB%20Xen%20HVM%20VPS%20in%20UK\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=TheHostHouse%20-%20%C2%A34.06%20512MB%